None
00:01:38,600 --> 00:01:40,360
"Ashes of Love"

None
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:42,240
"Episode 33"

None
00:01:43,260 --> 00:01:44,700
Dad, what are you going to do?

None
00:01:45,140 --> 00:01:47,420
Sui, you may be accidentally injured.

None
00:01:47,960 --> 00:01:48,880
Come over here.

None
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:15,860
Sui.

None
00:02:16,880 --> 00:02:17,600
Why are you

None
00:02:17,810 --> 00:02:19,800
so obsessive with someone

None
00:02:19,980 --> 00:02:21,680
who doesn’t love you?

None
00:02:23,540 --> 00:02:25,220
If he really cared about you,

None
00:02:25,720 --> 00:02:26,960
he would have married you.

None
00:02:33,700 --> 00:02:36,060
Ask them to step back or I won’t come there.

None
00:02:41,200 --> 00:02:42,000
Step back.

None
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:49,600
Come here.

None
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:51,840
Come to me.

None
00:03:36,420 --> 00:03:38,740
King Yi, see?

None
00:03:42,480 --> 00:03:43,720
My daughter is…

None
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:01,080
Sui.

None
00:04:02,860 --> 00:04:03,620
Dad,

None
00:04:05,620 --> 00:04:07,460
you were nice to me this life.

None
00:04:09,320 --> 00:04:10,520
I’ll keep it in mind.

None
00:04:13,720 --> 00:04:15,400
You’re a good dad,

None
00:04:18,780 --> 00:04:19,800
but it is a pity that

None
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:23,220
compared with Xu Feng,

None
00:04:25,540 --> 00:04:26,540
you’re nothing

None
00:04:28,840 --> 00:04:31,280
but a mere mortal.

None
00:04:40,660 --> 00:04:41,320
My Lord.

None
00:04:42,740 --> 00:04:43,320
My Lord.

None
00:04:46,540 --> 00:04:48,100
Sui. Sui.

None
00:04:49,280 --> 00:04:49,960
My Lord.

None
00:04:50,340 --> 00:04:51,020
My Lord.

None
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:57,780
My Lord. My Lord.

None
00:05:03,880 --> 00:05:05,240
Listen up,
everyone from Duke Nanping Mansion,

None
00:05:05,620 --> 00:05:07,040
if you put down your weapons right now

None
00:05:07,340 --> 00:05:08,800
and fight a battle following His Majesty,

None
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:10,470
you can expiate your crime by good deeds

None
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:12,320
and won’t be punished

None
00:05:12,340 --> 00:05:13,440
for assassinating His Majesty.

None
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:15,920
Or your nine clans will be killed.

None
00:05:16,640 --> 00:05:18,420
I didn’t know

None
00:05:18,420 --> 00:05:19,820
my dad would commit regicide.

None
00:05:20,820 --> 00:05:21,620
I…

None
00:05:23,940 --> 00:05:24,680
I…

None
00:05:58,880 --> 00:06:00,020
You have just repelled the army of Liangguo.

None
00:06:00,020 --> 00:06:01,080
Would you like to
rest for a night before you leave?

None
00:06:01,540 --> 00:06:02,360
Cousin.

None
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:04,360
Go.

None
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:12,960
Cousin.

None
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:16,720
My dad is dead.

None
00:06:18,560 --> 00:06:22,020
Now I can only depend on you.

None
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,260
I know.

None
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:27,200
I’ll keep what you did for Huaiwu

None
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:28,760
in my mind.

None
00:06:29,300 --> 00:06:30,500
If you meet any problems in the future,

None
00:06:31,100 --> 00:06:32,500
I won’t stand idly by.

None
00:06:33,140 --> 00:06:34,660
I have only one problem,

None
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:42,100
that is, I want you to marry me willingly.

None
00:06:43,860 --> 00:06:46,140
Do you still mind the affair
between Lord Puchi and me?

None
00:06:47,160 --> 00:06:48,700
That was a mistake.

None
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:51,800
My love for you is so true.

None
00:06:51,960 --> 00:06:54,040
I’ll marry no one but you this life.

None
00:06:54,520 --> 00:06:55,160
Sui He.

None
00:06:56,790 --> 00:06:58,120
Life is vain and
I’m just a passerby in the world.

None
00:06:58,400 --> 00:06:59,540
If you don’t promise me,

None
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:02,000
I don’t want to live anymore.

None
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:08,900
Sui He,

None
00:07:10,460 --> 00:07:11,840
I love someone

None
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:14,780
and can’t love others.

None
00:07:16,260 --> 00:07:17,300
So from today on,

None
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:20,320
I’ll treat you as my real sister.

None
00:07:22,100 --> 00:07:23,600
Do you love

None
00:07:26,320 --> 00:07:27,280
Jin Mi?

None
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:29,640
Yes.

None
00:07:32,020 --> 00:07:33,100
Why?

None
00:07:34,140 --> 00:07:35,720
She’s Saint Girl of Saint Doctors’ Family.

None
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:37,560
It’s impossible for you to marry her.

None
00:07:38,220 --> 00:07:38,920
Cousin.

None
00:07:39,840 --> 00:07:41,380
I fell in love with you since I was a child.

None
00:07:42,260 --> 00:07:43,680
I have done so much for you.

None
00:07:44,620 --> 00:07:45,660
I even killed dad…

None
00:07:47,660 --> 00:07:50,140
Why are you so cruel to me?

None
00:07:50,620 --> 00:07:51,500
Sui He.

None
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:53,900
I know your mind.

None
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:56,380
I’m grateful for

None
00:07:56,940 --> 00:07:58,200
what you’ve done for me,

None
00:07:59,659 --> 00:08:00,679
but

None
00:08:03,340 --> 00:08:05,039
it has also terrified me.

None
00:08:06,080 --> 00:08:07,600
I know I’m unable to repay your kindness.

None
00:08:08,460 --> 00:08:09,340
If you’re in danger

None
00:08:09,840 --> 00:08:11,100
in the future,

None
00:08:11,100 --> 00:08:12,040
I’ll protect you with my life.

None
00:08:12,760 --> 00:08:14,040
But I can by no means

None
00:08:15,620 --> 00:08:17,020
marry you.

None
00:08:22,940 --> 00:08:23,620
Cousin,

None
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:26,380
what I have done is all for you.

None
00:08:26,760 --> 00:08:28,800
What’s special about Jin Mi?

None
00:08:29,640 --> 00:08:32,380
You chase her both in heaven and earth.

None
00:08:32,380 --> 00:08:33,140
Sui He.

None
00:08:37,020 --> 00:08:38,860
You’re unstable after
so many things happened in these days.

None
00:08:40,040 --> 00:08:41,180
Let’s talk about it another day.

None
00:08:45,940 --> 00:08:47,080
Why haven’t you taken off
your amour yet, Your Majesty?

None
00:08:47,380 --> 00:08:48,260
Is the horse ready?

None
00:08:48,260 --> 00:08:49,060
Yes.

None
00:08:49,060 --> 00:08:50,060
I chose a team of elite soldiers

None
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:51,320
to escort you to the Villa.

None
00:08:51,460 --> 00:08:52,460
Send Princess back.

None
00:08:56,360 --> 00:09:00,400
Jin Mi, I won’t let you get what you want.

None
00:09:37,380 --> 00:09:38,120
Your Majesty.

None
00:09:41,920 --> 00:09:43,580
Am I dreaming again?

None
00:09:44,580 --> 00:09:45,580
No.

None
00:09:52,980 --> 00:09:53,860
You’re back.

None
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:56,880
I wanted to see you earlier.

None
00:09:58,000 --> 00:09:59,140
What’s wrong with you?

None
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:01,400
Qiang Huo said you got inflamed.

None
00:10:02,040 --> 00:10:02,780
You know

None
00:10:02,920 --> 00:10:04,360
I never believe in her medical skill.

None
00:10:05,420 --> 00:10:07,440
Moreover, you’re so weak now.

None
00:10:07,760 --> 00:10:09,280
I don’t believe you just got inflamed.

None
00:10:10,580 --> 00:10:11,920
Is it that you’re poisoned

None
00:10:11,920 --> 00:10:13,920
when you study those strange herbs?

None
00:10:16,140 --> 00:10:20,180
Jin Mi, you know your symptoms best.

None
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:23,020
Tell me what happened to you.

None
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:24,620
Your Majesty,

None
00:10:25,800 --> 00:10:27,800
although Qiang Huo is not as skilled as me,

None
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:30,380
she is a member of
Saint Doctors’ Family after all.

None
00:10:30,820 --> 00:10:31,880
I did

None
00:10:32,480 --> 00:10:33,600
get inflamed.

None
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:35,960
How come

None
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:37,160
you’re so weak

None
00:10:37,160 --> 00:10:38,440
and coughed so badly?

None
00:10:39,180 --> 00:10:40,440
I don’t know much about medicine,

None
00:10:41,040 --> 00:10:42,120
but you can’t lie to me.

None
00:10:43,600 --> 00:10:45,200
How dare I lie to you?

None
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:47,200
I actually

None
00:10:48,260 --> 00:10:51,360
have been prone to get inflamed
since I was a child.

None
00:10:51,620 --> 00:10:53,560
I may go faint after eating just one litchi,

None
00:10:54,040 --> 00:10:55,740
but I’m good at pharmacy,

None
00:10:56,040 --> 00:10:57,740
so I have developed

None
00:10:58,100 --> 00:10:59,100
a kind of medicine

None
00:10:59,420 --> 00:11:00,900
to cure this symptom once and for all.

None
00:11:01,580 --> 00:11:03,940
I just wanted to try it out,

None
00:11:04,420 --> 00:11:05,580
so I ate some longans.

None
00:11:05,740 --> 00:11:08,240
Unexpectedly, I passed out at once.

None
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:09,860
That’s embarrassing.

None
00:11:10,140 --> 00:11:11,100
Where is the medicine?

None
00:11:21,540 --> 00:11:22,520
How many tablets should you take?

None
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:28,820
Three ones.

None
00:11:36,620 --> 00:11:37,740
Take them.

None
00:12:01,220 --> 00:12:03,360
Lie down and have a good rest.

None
00:12:06,760 --> 00:12:09,640
Your Majesty, I didn’t lie to you, right?

None
00:12:11,020 --> 00:12:12,060
After taking the medicine,

None
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:13,640
I feel much better now.

None
00:12:14,220 --> 00:12:15,480
I’m all right.

None
00:12:15,720 --> 00:12:16,760
How about

None
00:12:17,800 --> 00:12:19,820
taking a walk in the courtyard

None
00:12:20,120 --> 00:12:22,700
or playing chess with you?

None
00:12:23,300 --> 00:12:24,440
Promise me

None
00:12:24,980 --> 00:12:26,660
you can’t scare me like that again.

None
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:33,860
Your Majesty,

None
00:12:34,520 --> 00:12:36,280
did you return from the battlefield directly?

None
00:12:38,020 --> 00:12:39,100
So what?

None
00:12:42,020 --> 00:12:44,580
I just heard that you’re God of War before,

None
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:46,180
but I have never

None
00:12:46,820 --> 00:12:48,620
seen you in martial attire.

None
00:12:50,320 --> 00:12:51,920
They’re right.

None
00:12:53,120 --> 00:12:54,140
You look handsome.

None
00:13:19,520 --> 00:13:21,700
Princess Sui He, what can I do for you?

None
00:13:23,120 --> 00:13:24,120
Send this letter

None
00:13:24,320 --> 00:13:26,120
to the monarch of Liangguo in person.

None
00:13:26,820 --> 00:13:29,400
I promise him that I’ll cooperate
with him in wiping out Huaiwu.

None
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:31,000
With this letter,

None
00:13:31,420 --> 00:13:33,180
the King of Liangguo will
definitely go out to battle in person.

None
00:13:33,580 --> 00:13:34,800
You must try every means

None
00:13:35,380 --> 00:13:37,440
to make sure that
no mistake is made this time.

None
00:13:41,100 --> 00:13:42,180
I did notice

None
00:13:42,180 --> 00:13:43,300
the smell of Mu Ci.

None
00:13:45,300 --> 00:13:45,960
Yes.

None
00:13:47,420 --> 00:13:49,060
Once the monarch of Liangguo
goes out to battle in person,

None
00:13:49,440 --> 00:13:51,060
Xu Feng will accept battle in person too.

None
00:13:51,540 --> 00:13:53,280
When he leaves Beiyuan Villa,

None
00:13:53,840 --> 00:13:55,280
you have to kill Jin Mi for me.

None
00:13:58,260 --> 00:14:00,060
It turns out that his target is Jin Mi.

None
00:14:00,220 --> 00:14:01,880
Even without Spirit-Vanishing Arrow,

None
00:14:02,460 --> 00:14:04,640
you should send her back to Heaven Realm
to restart experiencing hardships.

None
00:14:05,260 --> 00:14:06,440
I can hardly wait.

None
00:14:06,500 --> 00:14:07,360
Wait, Your Highness.

None
00:14:07,820 --> 00:14:09,380
Her Majesty ordered me

None
00:14:09,960 --> 00:14:11,380
to recover Spirit-Vanishing Arrow first.

None
00:14:11,940 --> 00:14:12,900
She worries that

None
00:14:13,060 --> 00:14:14,300
someone may harm the second Prince

None
00:14:14,360 --> 00:14:15,640
with this arrow.

None
00:14:15,640 --> 00:14:18,740
So does she know your arrangement?

None
00:14:19,520 --> 00:14:20,540
In this case,

None
00:14:21,380 --> 00:14:22,860
after sending the letter,

None
00:14:23,060 --> 00:14:24,260
go to protect Xu Feng.

None
00:14:24,460 --> 00:14:26,720
If anyone wants to hurt him
with Spirit-Vanishing Arrow,

None
00:14:27,060 --> 00:14:28,820
you can take the chance to take the arrow

None
00:14:29,060 --> 00:14:30,280
to kill Jin Mi.

None
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:32,280
Yes.

None
00:14:43,080 --> 00:14:44,300
It turns out that you left
without saying a word that day

None
00:14:44,580 --> 00:14:46,300
was to kill Jin Mi.

None
00:14:46,720 --> 00:14:47,860
She is my friend.

None
00:14:47,980 --> 00:14:49,520
I won’t allow you to hurt her.

None
00:14:52,320 --> 00:14:54,800
Mu Ci, what has happened
to you all these years?

None
00:14:54,860 --> 00:14:56,420
Why do you want to kill her?

None
00:14:57,200 --> 00:14:58,960
If you have any trouble, you can tell me.

None
00:14:59,360 --> 00:15:00,320
I’ll help you.

None
00:15:05,020 --> 00:15:06,180
If you insist on killing her,

None
00:15:06,360 --> 00:15:07,440
you are my enemy.

None
00:15:18,940 --> 00:15:19,960
That’s better.

None
00:15:54,260 --> 00:15:56,180
Why is there the smell
of my bones and blood here?

None
00:16:15,840 --> 00:16:16,680
Luckily,

None
00:16:17,100 --> 00:16:18,520
Spirit-Vanishing Arrow is hanging here,

None
00:16:18,800 --> 00:16:20,340
but it doesn’t hurt the second Princess.

None
00:16:22,700 --> 00:16:25,360
Jin Mi, I’m sorry.

None
00:16:25,540 --> 00:16:26,940
It’s my fault.

None
00:16:28,800 --> 00:16:29,660
Jin Mi.

None
00:16:33,280 --> 00:16:34,619
You must be crazy

None
00:16:34,940 --> 00:16:36,800
to take three tablets of Wu Yin.

None
00:16:38,220 --> 00:16:40,040
Only it can suppress

None
00:16:41,500 --> 00:16:43,140
the syndrome of Qing Yue.

None
00:16:43,140 --> 00:16:45,020
But it’s also poisonous.

None
00:16:45,480 --> 00:16:48,400
Taking such a deadly poison, you’ll die.

None
00:16:49,119 --> 00:16:51,339
I have only some time to stay with him.

None
00:16:53,760 --> 00:16:56,040
I don’t want him to see my sickly look

None
00:16:57,300 --> 00:16:59,260
and worry about me

None
00:17:01,040 --> 00:17:02,640
when he is with me.

None
00:17:06,020 --> 00:17:06,800
In the past,

None
00:17:07,180 --> 00:17:09,800
I thought you were
the smartest person in the world,

None
00:17:10,520 --> 00:17:11,800
but now to me

None
00:17:11,880 --> 00:17:14,060
you’re totally a fool.

None
00:17:19,520 --> 00:17:20,240
Jin Mi.

None
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:22,620
Jin Mi.

None
00:17:24,480 --> 00:17:25,160
Jin Mi.

None
00:17:32,580 --> 00:17:33,680
Your Majesty.

None
00:17:34,940 --> 00:17:35,860
Your Majesty,

None
00:17:36,540 --> 00:17:38,160
Saint Girl is getting changed.

None
00:17:38,220 --> 00:17:40,140
Please wait for a while in the courtyard.

None
00:17:41,300 --> 00:17:42,140
OK.

None
00:18:04,540 --> 00:18:05,320
Your Majesty,

None
00:18:14,140 --> 00:18:15,520
you’re going to the front line again.

None
00:18:16,680 --> 00:18:18,180
Originally, I thought
after we defeated Liangguo,

None
00:18:18,360 --> 00:18:20,180
they would take no action in a short time.

None
00:18:20,980 --> 00:18:22,180
However, it’s out of expectation that

None
00:18:22,360 --> 00:18:24,580
the King of Liangguo will fight personally,

None
00:18:26,300 --> 00:18:29,560
so I have to accept battle again.

None
00:18:30,640 --> 00:18:31,560
Your Majesty,

None
00:18:33,080 --> 00:18:33,960
I…

None
00:18:34,700 --> 00:18:36,460
I’m afraid I can’t wait for you.

None
00:18:36,920 --> 00:18:39,880
What? You can’t wait for these few days?

None
00:18:46,280 --> 00:18:47,240
Originally, I thought

None
00:18:47,880 --> 00:18:49,240
as you were so stubborn before,

None
00:18:49,640 --> 00:18:51,240
we had to wait for all this life.

None
00:18:51,400 --> 00:18:52,740
I thought the happiest time in my life

None
00:18:52,740 --> 00:18:53,840
would come after we died

None
00:18:53,840 --> 00:18:56,140
and were buried
in the emperor’s tomb together.

None
00:18:56,640 --> 00:18:57,680
But now

None
00:18:58,260 --> 00:18:59,440
you’re willing to wait for me

None
00:18:59,620 --> 00:19:01,100
and create future with me.

None
00:19:01,660 --> 00:19:04,360
Happiness comes so fast

None
00:19:04,640 --> 00:19:05,860
that it’s like a dream.

None
00:19:08,320 --> 00:19:09,120
Jin Mi,

None
00:19:10,420 --> 00:19:12,360
do you really want to be with me

None
00:19:12,940 --> 00:19:14,160
and be my queen forever?

None
00:19:24,960 --> 00:19:25,900
I do.

None
00:19:28,200 --> 00:19:30,020
But how about your promise to the people?

None
00:19:30,260 --> 00:19:31,900
You said you won’t get married

None
00:19:33,140 --> 00:19:34,360
before unifying the state.

None
00:19:35,500 --> 00:19:37,880
This is just nonsense.

None
00:19:38,480 --> 00:19:40,440
It was just because
you were so stubborn back then

None
00:19:40,560 --> 00:19:42,060
that I used it as an excuse

None
00:19:42,220 --> 00:19:43,420
to refuse the officials.

None
00:19:44,020 --> 00:19:45,080
But I really want to

None
00:19:45,420 --> 00:19:47,080
declare to the world

None
00:19:47,640 --> 00:19:49,080
and let everyone know

None
00:19:49,560 --> 00:19:50,860
you’re my queen now.

None
00:19:57,560 --> 00:19:58,940
Since I’ve promised you,

None
00:19:59,820 --> 00:20:01,400
I’ll always wait for you here.

None
00:20:03,940 --> 00:20:06,860
Aren’t you going to make a plan

None
00:20:07,120 --> 00:20:09,140
to help me get rid of the status of Saint Girl?

None
00:20:10,240 --> 00:20:11,540
We have a whole life,

None
00:20:12,600 --> 00:20:13,640
so don’t be hasty now.

